{
  "stem": "1721.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I had no idea.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Exactly.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That lasted a few months.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think she recognized that I was able to be able to handle it on my own.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I pretty well blended in fairly nicely and was able to learn English, stay with my school.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, at that point, I forgot what grade they put me in, but I think I remember they had to put me in a couple of earlier grades just to get started.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then when I was probably 13, 12, 13, I was already jumped in, and I was already caught up in my regular grades.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So, the native intelligence was there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was just a matter of me translating it into the English way of life, the American way of life.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So, then I just moved OK into that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So, I wasn't held back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I wasn't sitting in a kindergarten class when I was older.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then I learned English fairly quickly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Picked it up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I spoke very little German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I refused.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I had a lot of problems.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The war, I think the experiences, it affected my parents, my stepfather, my mother tremendously.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The experience that they went through-- I think my stepfather went through some very bad in Buchenwald and Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he saw a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He never talked about it at all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I never knew anything while I was living with them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They never discussed anything, even though I know they went through it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I know that my mother went through a lot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was just never a discussion.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Whenever it came up with other survivors, they would just shut up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They would never enter-- they would never join in the conversations.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
